## DECLARATION & ATTENDING THE ALTAR

IM: (_I._M. uncovers head._) In the name of God and
   Adoniram, I declare {{blank 6em}} Council No. {{blank 2em}},
   Cryptic Masons closed on the Royal Master Degree in
   form. (_I._M. recovers._) Companion Conductor of the
   Council, close the Great Lights.

Note: C._C. advances to altar, squaring corners, removes
   the Square and Compasses, closes the Volume of the
   Sacred Law, and returns to station without saluting.

## INFORMING THE SENTINEL

IM: Companion Captain of the Guard, inform the Sentinel.
CG: Companion Steward, inform the Sentinel.

Note: Without saluting, the Steward goes to the door
  and gives ●●● ●●● ●● to call up the Sentinel. |
  The Sentinel acknowledges by returning the same |
  ●●● ●●● ●●.

Stew: (_Opens door._) Companion Sentinel, this Council is
  closed on the Royal Master Degree in form. (_Door may
  remain open at this point. Steward returns to station
  and faces C._G. without saluting._) Companion Captain
  of the Guard, your order has been obeyed.
CG: (_Without saluting._) Illustrious Master, your order has
  been obeyed.
IM: ●

